posting_body: ['1-BR APARTMENT LISTINGS:', '1BR units available at 902 Grand Avenue and 908 Grand Avenue, Saint Paul, MN 55105:', "Call today, these units won't last long!", ' Apartments available July, August, and September (call for details based on your move date)', '-- $940 - $1,040/mo', '-- 1st or 2nd floor or Garden Level', '-- Tenants pay electricity and stove gas.', ' Property owner pays radiator heat and water!', '-- Great lease terms!', 'Flexible or Fixed.', 'Quoted rents are for a 9-12 month fixed term lease.', 'Additional $25/mo for flexible term.', '-- Smoke-Free!!', ' All leases prohibit smoking, candles, and incense anywhere inside the building or on the property outside.', '-- Permit on-street parking', 'On Grand Avenue just 3/4 of a block to 1 block west of Victoria!', ' Great Location to everything!!!', ' #GreatForMitchellHamlineStudents #GreatForMitchellStudents', '** We are a family run business, not a big management company, who really cares for our buildings and the tenants so you will receive personal attention and care if you choose to rent from us.', 'Our units feature:', '- 1-BR, LR, Kitchen, Bath, Dining Area //', 'Approx 650 sq ft', '- Hardwood floors.', ' Carpeted garden level unit.', '- Laundry and storage in basement common area', 'For more information and to set up a time to see the available units, please contact the property managers directly and reference this CL ad:', 'Alisa or Brenna', 'Day:', 'show contact info', 'Evening:', 'show contact info', 'Email: See above "reply to" link.', 'Website: www.apts.cc']
